{"tid":1628693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請罷買所有用余文樂做代言人的品牌","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:46:44.000Z","uid":104034,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1630e2d633c74187c2389d8fff452185ba886330","tid":1628693,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"1. Tommy Hilfige<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbmW5sh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbmW5sh.jpg&h=bce72edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. Bose<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwSOWyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwSOWyZ.jpg&h=b52d1f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>余文樂微博表態「反暴力」後首更新IG 父子齊高舉勝利手勢</strong><br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》修訂的風波仍然持續，除引起多場集會、示威，不少演藝名人亦有紛紛表態，其中余文樂早前（5/8）在微博發文，指自己反對暴力：「最近香港發生很多事，我作為一個土生土長的香港人，看到那麼多憤怒與暴力感到很痛心，一個人的立場並不能代表其他人，就像一小眾破壞秩序的人不能代表全香港的人，香港已經回歸了22年了，香港是中國的一部份，我是中國人，這一點無需多言，我不認同也不支持所有違法的人與事，希望香港盡快恢復秩序。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3172187/org/f310f73db74b54ab627322bf67d02dd9.jpg/9bez8cPFw7GYM75CVq31DtndCAjWu45n9Hi2pfR4tqU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3172187%2Forg%2Ff310f73db74b54ab627322bf67d02dd9.jpg%2F9bez8cPFw7GYM75CVq31DtndCAjWu45n9Hi2pfR4tqU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=041a000b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf162ce0d681305883a8f65bd6e5283cb68dd514","tid":1628693,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc52f25e164c678512b52481a8b7207a1e22c3c3","tid":1628693,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288db19e488ef8ec9859b5f61a63473ac7cb94d4","tid":1628693,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":