d":1628693,"uid":104034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國藝人余文樂堅稱，在火箭總經理Daryl Morey的Twitter戶口留言的是冒認他身分的同名戶口。不過，《蘋果日報》體育版總編輯仙道彬在個人Facebook專頁稱，該Twitter帳號（lok666real）經《蘋果》娛樂版編輯查證，的確屬於余文樂所有。<br />\n<br />\n而且，該帳戶上載體育品牌及贊助商New Balance的宣傳影片，以及他多張工作照片。值得留意的是，該戶口在消息傳出後只刪除兩個侮辱Daryl Morey的留言。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qh2SDQ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqh2SDQ9.jpg&h=079a46df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81242389111f2d45763c7b5e1426adca8aa2d8cb","tid":1628693,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍擺 黃幫"},{"pid":"b52fee0762a3a0cfed711a0a8b1871f9b23ceb31","tid":1628693,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思想重推！麻煩入一入黎睇下你既角色定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［我有野講］咪撚再唱歌叫口號［入黎睇下自己衰咩］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612280</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"604a26c573ffe68f9371f061cf621c74b3e9ac03","tid":1628693,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"仲有New Balance ！<br />\n成日同佢聯名仲要做埋大中華區代言人"},{"pid":"2423605f83f145cc5cfa5b6beb04ccc1c650466b","tid":1628693,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"604a26c573ffe68f9371f061cf621c74b3e9ac03","tid":1628693,"uid":136342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"仲有New Balance ！<br />\n成日同佢聯名仲要做埋大中華區代言人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>3. New Balance</strong><br />\n<br />\n余文樂MADNESS聯名New Balance開賣日期曝光<br />\n<br />\n 「六叔」余文樂是許多潮男的穿搭指標，也讓主理潮牌MADNESS每個動作都備受關注。而全新與New Balance聯名的鞋款，即將在4月27日開賣，消息一釋出立刻引起眾多網友熱論，只不過想購買還不簡單，還要能符合「條件」！<br />\n<br />\nNew Balance官方臉書宣布，將於27日在敦化門市超限量發售，中午12點30分前，排隊者需穿著「英美製99X系列鞋款」方能投籤，每人一籤，不得代領。下午2點就會於現場公布中籤名單與後補名單。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eyu2gJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyu2gJZ.jpg&h=dd4b268f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681c8f043e28dc8476a0130afbdb7259b698bd8a","tid":1628693,"uid":104034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}